# Secrets / credentials — NEVER commit. The Anthropic API key lives in your shell
# env (~/.zshenv), not the repo; these patterns are defense-in-depth for the
# automated daily cadence that pushes to a PUBLIC repo.
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
.netrc
*credentials*
*.token

